@node Requirements "System requirements"

@{b}	System requirements
	=-----------------=
@{ub}

        o Amiga with kick 3.0 or higher (sorry, a 2.0 version will come soon).
        o Overdrive CD-Rom or compatible.
	o Version *9* of the cd.device (OverCD-handler) that comes with Overdrive.
	  (only needed when used with Overdrive/Zappo)
@endnode


