@node Distribution "Distribution of this software"

@{b}	Distribution
	=----------=
@{ub}
	Interplay is @{b}NOT@{ub} Public Domain, but you may spread it as you
	like. Interplay may be put on non-profit PD archives like
	Fred-Fish, AmiNet etc, but we would like you to contact us if
	you do wish to include it in your compilation! 

	If you like this program and want it to be developed, please mail
	us and tell us you like it. Or you could call, snail or whatever..


	This program package must only be spread with its full contents.

	/Interplay2.0/s/@{b}Interplay.list@{ub}
	/Interplay2.0/Docs/@{b}Interplay.guide@{ub}
	/Interplay2.0/@{b}Interplay@{ub}
	/Interplay2.0/@{b}Interplay.info@{ub}

@endnode


